---

<SubPageLayout
  title="財務業務資訊"
  titleEn="Investor Zone"
  titleTw="投資人專區"
  menuItems={menuItems}
  activeId="financial"
  pageClass="financial_page"
>
  <!-- 年度及期中報告 -->
  <section class="mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary border-b-2 border-gold pb-2 mb-6">{langData[19].tw}</h2>
    <div class="space-y-6">
      {reports.map((group) => (
        <details class="group border border-gray-200 rounded-lg" open>
          <summary class="px-6 py-4 cursor-pointer font-bold text-primary hover:text-gold transition-colors flex justify-between items-center">
            {group.title}
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path></svg>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-6 pb-4 space-y-2">
            {group.files.map((file) => (
              <a href={file.href} target="_blank" class="block text-primary/70 hover:text-gold transition-colors py-1">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 inline mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 10v6m0 0l-3-3m3 3l3-3m2 8H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"></path></svg>
                {file.name}
              </a>
            ))}
          </div>
        </details>
      ))}
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 重大訊息 -->
  <section>
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary border-b-2 border-gold pb-2 mb-6">{langData[20].tw}</h2>
    <div class="prose max-w-none">
      <h4>重大訊息</h4>
      <p>寶得利國際股份有限公司係於1990年6月於中華民國證券櫃檯買賣中心掛牌上櫃 (股票代號: 5301)，投資相關資訊請至公開資訊觀測站網站參閱 查詢頁面請依下述步驟 公司代號：5301→ 年度：110年 → 月份：全年度 → 搜尋</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</SubPageLayout>
